title: "What to Know About the Latest China Chip Restrictions as the U.S. Cracks Down"
text: "The stocks of microchip and semiconductor companies are volatile today on reports that the Biden administration is moving to strengthen chip restrictions on China. The administration is closing loopholes that have enabled American chipmakers to skirt current laws and continue selling their products to China."
